modules.description: This module handles document metadata management, bibliography processing, and structured content generation. It operates on document trees, path-to-entry maps, and XML/HTML buffers using types like `auto_id_spec` and `Stog.Html.XR` for cross-reference resolution and auto-ID generation. Key use cases include compiling documents with dynamic bibliographies, formatting citations in XML/HTML output, and maintaining consistent tagging across document transformations.
